Package uhh_lt.newsleak.writer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ElasticsearchDocumentWriter
    A writer to populate a temporary elasticsearch index with fulltexts from a prior annotation chain.
    NewsleakTimeFormatter
    Extraction and formatting of dates and date ranges as annotated by HeidelTime to be used for temporal filtering in newsleak.
    PostgresDbWriter
    A writer to populate the newsleak postgres database with final fulltexts and extracted entities from a prior annotation chain.
    TextLineWriter
    A simple writer for debug and development purposes only.
